 be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty has made lawful silk and gold for the women of my nation, but he has forbidden them for men.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 5265 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5692,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/30\/haram-cut-animals-alive\/","url_meta":{"origin":5680,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Animals: Cutting animals while alive is forbidden","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 30, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Waqid al-Layth reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhatever is cut from an animal while it is alive is unlawful carrion.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"This is acted upon by the people of knowledge.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1480 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0642\u0650\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u064a\u0652\u062b\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6174,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/best-food-earned-hard-work\/","url_meta":{"origin":5680,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Independence: Best food to eat earned by hard work","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most wholesome food a man can eat is that which he has earned.\" Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 4397 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0637\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5680","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5680"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5680\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/medi